  section.how-it-works--section
    .row
      .how-it-works--caption
        h3.capitalized.capitalized--lite How it Works
        h2 Grow your money with compound interest
        p.
          
          You start by investing in any of our investment package, where we take things a step further by helping you earn interest on your invested funds.
          
    .row
      .col-1-of-2
        .how-it-works--investment-type
