    .row
      h2 Benefits of our professionally managed funds
    .row
      .col-1-of-2
        .benefits--benefit
          h3 High ROI.
          p.
            
            You earn minimum of 28% or more of your investment on our Funds Management plans or 17% every month for five(5) months on our Lending Investment Plan.
            
        .benefits--benefit
          h3 No maintance fees.
          p.
            
            There are no hidden or extra charges for investment. All of our transactions and commissions are stated clearly for you at the very beginning.
            
        .benefits--benefit
          h3 Invest as you go.
          p.
            
            With our flexible investment plans (FIP), We've made it possible for anyone to invest a certain amount of your income and earn returns on a periodic basis.
            
      .col-1-of-2
        figure.benefits--img
          img(src="assets/benefits_image (2).png", alt)
